<title>USA: Centex adopts new shareholder rights plan.</title>
<headline>Centex adopts new shareholder rights plan.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1996-10-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Centex Corp said Wednesday it has adopted a new stockholder rights plan to replace the one that expired October 1.</p>
<p>The company did not disclose the terms of the rights plan.</p>
<p>It is to be exercised only if an individual or group were to acquire 15 percent or more of Centex's outstanding common stock, or announces an offer to acquire 15 percent or more of Centex's common stock.</p>
<p>The company did not immediately return a telephone call.</p>
